* {{i-c|having great duration}} [[extended]], [[lengthy]], [[prolonged]]

=====Antonyms=====
* {{i-c|having much distance from one point to another}} [[low]] {{italbrac|vertically upwards}}, [[shallow]] {{italbrac|vertically upwards or downwards}}, [[short]]
* {{i-c|having great duration}} [[brief]], [[short]]

